5
00:01:01,963 --> 00:01:03,353
20 minút.

6
00:01:03,594 --> 00:01:06,841
Ktovie, koľko to asi trvá odtiaľ.

7
00:02:18,334 --> 00:02:20,267
To bude asi ono.

8
