Už si hore?

53
00:08:04,214 --> 00:08:05,369
Tu si?

54
00:08:07,653 --> 00:08:08,769
Aký je film?

55
00:08:10,484 --> 00:08:11,882
Sleduj sám.

56
00:08:12,153 --> 00:08:16,078
Blíži sa vyvrcholenie.

57
00:08:23,504 --> 00:08:25,802
