59
00:08:29,574 --> 00:08:33,558
čo je dosť času na to,
aby spáchal zločin a stihol sa vrátiť.

60
00:08:36,813 --> 00:08:38,505
Takže to bol naozaj Yoo Beom Jin?

61
00:08:41,354 --> 00:08:45,293
Ale nemáme to ako dokázať.

62
00:08:45,293 --> 00:08:46,582
Prečo by sme nemali?

63
00:08:47,194 --> 00:08:49,662
Je tu Tae Ra,
ktorá s ním v tom kine bola.

64
00:08:50,263 --> 00:08:54,403
Ak sa z akéhokoľvek dôvodu
na hodinu vyparil,

65
00:08:54,403 --> 00:08:58,085
nie je možné, aby si to nevšimla.

66
00:09:00,133 --> 00:09:01,290
Takže...

67
00:09:01,374 --> 00:09:03,338
Jedine Han Tae Ra to môže dokázať.

68
00:09:03,444 --> 00:09:05,244
Fakt, že Yoo Beom Jin

69
00:09:05,244 --> 00:09:08,188
nemal v čase Soo Ahinej vraždy

70
00:09:08,883 --> 00:09:10,130
žiadne alibi.

71
00:09:34,173 --> 00:09:36,441
(Nemocnica Donghan)

72
00:09:38,244 --> 00:09:41,855
Ako sa Soo Ah dostala na našu školu?

73
00:09:46,783 --> 00:09:49,883
Vari riaditeľ Lee Tae Seok...

74
00:09:49,883 --> 00:09:51,182
(Hye Soo)

75
00:09:53,324 --> 00:09:54,410
Prepáč mi.

76
00:09:57,124 --> 00:09:58,249
Áno, Hye Soo.

77
00:10:02,263 --> 00:10:03,753
Čo sa to udialo?

78
00:10:04,273 --> 00:10:05,420
Han Tae Ra je mŕtva?

79
00:10:08,474 --> 00:10:09,590
