95
00:12:07,594 --> 00:12:09,153
Dal som vám aj poslednú šancu.

96
00:12:09,364 --> 00:12:11,358
Keby ste ma boli počúvli,

97
00:12:11,393 --> 00:12:12,984
Han Tae Ra nemusela zomrieť.

98
00:12:16,734 --> 00:12:17,889
Povedz mi pravdu, ty sviňa.

99
00:12:18,874 --> 00:12:22,454
Keby ste sa tu neobjavili,
bolo by nám dobre.

100
00:12:22,704 --> 00:12:25,072
Boli by sme priateľmi,
akoby sa nič nebolo stalo.

101
00:12:27,173 --> 00:12:28,413
Hovor pravdu!

102
00:12:28,413 --> 00:12:31,013
To platí aj pre Soo Ah.
Keby nebolo jej,

103
00:12:31,013 --> 00:12:33,109
