160
00:16:00,954 --> 00:16:03,726
ju zabil a postaral sa,
aby to vyzeralo ako samovražda.

161
00:16:06,094 --> 00:16:09,442
Ale ako mohol zabiť svoju priateľku?

162
00:16:09,633 --> 00:16:10,850
Povedal mi,

163
00:16:11,204 --> 00:16:12,996
že keby som ho bol počúvol,

164
00:16:15,143 --> 00:16:16,633
Tae Ra by nezomrela.

165
00:16:17,844 --> 00:16:19,536
Keby som neprišiel do školy,

166
00:16:21,744 --> 00:16:23,101
nič by sa nebolo stalo

167
