337
00:28:55,484 --> 00:28:56,600
Budem čakať.

338
00:29:43,593 --> 00:29:44,719
Tak ako?

339
00:29:45,294 --> 00:29:47,056
Vydržte chvíľu.

340
00:29:47,363 --> 00:29:50,236
Myslím, že potrebuje nejaký čas.

341
00:30:09,954 --> 00:30:12,363
(Jung Soo Ah)

342
00:30:15,264 --> 00:30:17,390
